votebox.events

Class VoteBoxEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • votebox.events.VoteBoxEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAnnounceEvent

    public class VoteBoxEvent
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAnnounceEvent
    Event that represents the votebox message:
     (votebox label votebox-status battery-health protected-count public-count)
    See https://sys.cs.rice.edu/votebox/trac/wiki/VotingMessages for a complete list of messages.
